# Frontend Storybook (`apps/storybook`)

Visual workshop for `@repo/design-system`. App wiring: `frontend-app.mdc`. Layers: `agent-discipline.mdc`.

## Scope (stay here for visual work)

- Component previews and design-system galleries
- Theme/decorator tweaks for story context — not production route changes
- Story-specific mocks and parameters

Do **not** refactor `packages/design-system/components/ui/**` for Storybook contrast or polish. Fix preview decorators, parameters, or story layout instead.

## Story conventions

- CSF3 stories; co-locate decorators when a story needs shell chrome
- Semantic design tokens in story `className` — no ad-hoc hex or raw pixel hacks
- Import components from `@repo/design-system` — do not duplicate primitives in stories

## Anti-patterns

- Changing shadcn primitive defaults to match a story experiment
- Copy-pasting design-system component source into stories
- Editing `globals.css` tokens for one story's contrast

## Verification

```bash
pnpm --filter storybook typecheck
pnpm --filter storybook build    # before large story additions
```

Dev: `pnpm --filter storybook dev` (port 6006).
